<h3>Account Creation Help</h3>
<ul class="cerad_common_help">
    <li>User Display Name - This is what will show up at the top of the screen when you signin.</li>
    <li>User Name - You can use this to signin instead of a social network.</li>
    <li>User Email - This can also be used for signing in.  
        It's also used for password recovery.  
        Please use a valid email and please monitor the email account as the tournament approaches.
    </li>
    <li>User Password - Used when signing in without a social network.</li>
</ul>
